<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=shotsie39&buddyTimeStamp=20051003&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fmillsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fprocess_buddy.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1193060353&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit', 'transparent');</script></span>
Meet <b>Mika</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Mika lives at <a href='/home/?user=shotsie39'>70481 Castle Hill</a>, in one of Westridge's most elegant houses.  She has lived in Millsberry since March 5, 2005, and she's still making all sorts of new discoveries about the town!<br><br>One of Mika's most striking qualities is her charming personality.  She has the rare ability to start up a friendly conversation with almost anyone, and she enjoys having a large circle of friends at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/">Millsberry Academy</a>.  Mika's charm also comes in handy when she performs on stage, which is one of her favorite hobbies.  A devoted actress, Mika knows just how to catch the interest of an audience and draw them into the story.<br><br>Another part of what makes Mika a successful actress is her expressiveness.  She is very good at revealing her inner feelings with a simple facial expression.  This quality allows her performances as an actress to be very riveting, plus it also helps Mika with one of her other hobbies - singing.  Because she's so expressive, Mika knows just how to fill her music and lyrics with emotion and meaning.  Mika recently decided to share her sensitive, thoughtful music with all of Millsberry by recording some tracks at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/studio/">Recording Studio</a>.  Her touching voice has really struck a chord with a lot of listeners, taking her all the way to the top of the Cinnamon Toast Crunch Top Ten chart.<br><br>When she's not creating her own music, Mika can usually be found checking out other artists' work at a record shop.  Her favorite styles are pop, salsa, and world music, but she loves to explore all kinds of different sounds.  Mika's curiosity doesn't end with music, though.  She's always trying out new things, whether it's daring pink, black, and green fashions at a mall, an unusual pizza topping at a pizza place, or even a new game at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/arcade.phtml">Millsberry Arcade</a>!  Mika's curious nature has certainly helped her to fill out her trophy collection.   In addition to having fun while playing games, she has also won trophies for <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=13">Hop-N-Drop</a>, <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=19">Peabody Park Clean Up</a>, <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=18">Peanut Butter Toast Crunch Swirl</a>, <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=140">Sink the Three</a>, and <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=180">Galactic Defender</a>.  Mika's inquiring mind has surely kept her busy! <br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Mika, and congratulations on being Millsberry's Citizen of the Week!</div>
